emacs-hyperspec
****************

`emacs-hyperspec.el' provides local Common Lisp HyperSpec lookup commands
for Emacs.

The module is designed to be quiet at Emacs startup.  Loading it does not
probe HTTP URLs, run `wget', read the HyperSpec symbol map, or install
anything.  CLHS discovery and `Data/Map_Sym.txt' parsing are delayed until
the first lookup command needs them.

