Installation
************

Installation is explicit because it can perform network access.

`M-x pjb-clhs-install-quicklisp'
     Start an asynchronous Quicklisp install of the `clhs' system.  The
     command runs the program named by `pjb-clhs-lisp-command' and opens
     output in the `*clhs-install*' buffer.

After installation finishes, run `M-x clhs' again.  The next lookup will
discover the installed CLHS from Quicklisp.

Automatic prompting can be enabled by setting `pjb-clhs-auto-install' to
non-nil, but the default is nil so that lookup never starts network work
unless explicitly requested.


