Variables
*********

`common-lisp-hyperspec-root'
     The CLHS root URL.  It starts as nil.  After successful discovery it is
     set to a `file://' URL ending at the HyperSpec directory.

`common-lisp-hyperspec-symbols'
     The cached symbol table built from `Data/Map_Sym.txt'.  It starts as
     nil and is populated lazily.

`common-lisp-hyperspec-browser'
     Browser used for CLHS pages.  The default is `eww'.  Bind or set this
     to another `browse-url' browser function if desired.

`pjb-clhs-quicklisp-directory'
     Quicklisp root directory used for CLHS discovery.  The default is
     `~/quicklisp/'.

`pjb-clhs-lisp-command'
     Common Lisp command used by `pjb-clhs-install-quicklisp'.  The default
     is `sbcl'.

`pjb-clhs-auto-install'
     When non-nil, a failed lookup offers to start the Quicklisp install.
     The default nil keeps lookup non-networking unless the install command
     is run explicitly.

`*clhs-map-sym*'
     Relative path to the CLHS symbol map, normally `Data/Map_Sym.txt'.


